  <summary date="2021-08-04T18:29:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Gluten in Medicine Disclosure Act of 2019

This bill prohibits the sale of any drug intended for human use that contains an ingredient derived from a gluten-containing grain unless the drug's label (1)states that the drug contains such an ingredient, and (2)identifies the type of grain from which the ingredient is derived.</summary>
